description:
Snubull is a well looked after Pokémon who belongs to a wealthly lady called Madame Muchmoney.
Madame Muchmoney spoils and pampers Snubull a great deal. However, the Snubull wanted more freedom and frequently ran away from home only to be caught by Muchmoney`s butlers. After seeing how much Snubull enjoyed itself when it battled Meowth, Jessie, James and their Pokémon, Madame Muchmoney money tried to please Snubull by building an outdoor park. Snubull had fond memories of biting onto Meowth`s tale and left the park to pursue it.
name: Bulu (Kaneyo)
